Django

Django is a high-level Python web framework used to build **secure, scalable, and fast web applications**.

ğŸ‘‰ It follows MVT architecture** (Modelâ€“Viewâ€“Template)

| Component    | Purpose                           |
| ------------ | --------------------------------- |
|   Model      | Handles database (data structure) |
|   View       | Contains business logic           |
|   Template   | Frontend (HTML UI)                |

ğŸ“Œ Django is used for: Websites, Admin panels, APIs, Dashboards, E-commerce, etc.

