## ğŸ–¥ï¸ Running Development Server

Start server:

```bash
python manage.py runserver
```

Default:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/
```

Run on different port:

```bash
python manage.py runserver 8080
```

Stop server: CTRL + C

